{"id":35769,"date":"2023-12-07T14:13:56","date_gmt":"2023-12-07T22:13:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/?page_id=35769"},"modified":"2023-12-08T08:01:49","modified_gmt":"2023-12-08T16:01:49","slug":"high-performance-digital-advertising-for-software-and-high-tech","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/high-performance-digital-advertising-for-software-and-high-tech\/","title":{"rendered":"PPC Agency for Technology Companies"},"content":{"rendered":"\r\n<h1>\r\n\t\tHigh Performance Digital Advertising for Software and Tech Companies\r\n\t<\/h1>\r\n\t<p>Nowspeed creates and manages winning Google PPC, Microsoft Bing, LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram and Twitter Ad campaigns for software and technology companies. Ask us about a complimentary audit of your account to see how much more effective your campaigns can be!<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFREE AUDIT\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t\tFree 15-Point Digital Advertising Audit for Software and Tech Companies!\r\n\t<\/h2>\r\n\t<p>Do you want to find out how to create a winning digital advertising program? Fill out the form to schedule your free audit.<\/p>\r\n<p>For qualified software and technology companies, we will review your PPC strategy, dig into your campaign structure, look under the hood at your keywords, and review a dozen other factors that impact the success of your campaigns. This audit will identify key issues and help us both understand how we can improve your results.<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Computer-Screen-Marketing-1.png\" alt=\"Digital Advertising\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"907\" width=\"1162\" title=\"Computer-Screen-Marketing (1)\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t\tHigh Performance Digital Advertising for Software and Technology Companies!\r\n\t<\/h2>\r\n\t<p>Nowspeed creates and manages integrated digital advertising campaigns that drive profitable results for software and technology clients. Our strategic approach, comprehensive analytics, talented staff, and powerful methodology allow us to supercharge your campaigns. We&#8217;ve managed over $150MM in ad budget and have a track record of improving results by more than 50% for many clients.<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFree Audit and 90 Day Digital Ad Roadmap\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t\tWe lead with Experience and Validate with Data  \r\n\t<\/h2>\r\n\t<p>We start every new software or technology client relationship with a deep dive into all aspects of your ad campaigns. We&#8217;ll review your strategy, look under the hood at your campaign analytics and settings, and dig deep into your budget allocation, content, offers, landing pages, ad messages and competitors. The audit and 90 Day Plan we provide will make it clear that we can improve your results.<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/free-digital-marketing-audit\/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFREE AUDIT\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2.jpg\" alt=\"Experience and Validate with Data\" itemprop=\"image\" height=\"815\" width=\"950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2.jpg 950w, https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2-300x257.jpg 300w, https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Image-2-768x659.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px\" title=\"Validate with Data\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"  \/>\r\n\t<meta itemscope itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/WebPage\" itemid=\"https:\/\/nowspeed.com\/testimonials\/we-had-a-great-relationship-with-nowspeed\/\" content=\"We ha